  "title": "Cleaner",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>General office housekeeping duties such as vacuum, sweeping, mopping</li>\n  <li>Cleaning and sanitation of workspaces and display shelves</li>\n  <li>Washing of toilets (male and female)</li>\n  <li>Empty trash bin</li>\n  <li>Cleaning of common areas e.g. staircase, corridor, pantry areas</li>\n  <li>Wiping of glass doors, interior window and mirrors</li>\n  <li>Restock supplies such as tissue paper, hand soap, and cleaning products</li>\n  <li>Ensure all cleaning equipment is properly used, stored, and maintained</li>\n  <li>Follow health and safety guidelines in the handling of cleaning supplies</li>\n  <li>Outdoor sweeping required</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc cleaning duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year cleaning experience</li>\n  <li>Physically fit and able to handle cleaning tasks</li>\n  <li>Comfortable with toilet cleaning</li>\n  <li>Singaporeans preferred</li>\n  <li>5.5 work days</li>\n</ul>",
